  "texts": [
    "It can significantly reduce the processing time and enhance classification performance, especially for tiny datasets or images with complicated backgrounds.",
    "• A new architecture of Residual connections: the residual connections in ResNets with SE attention allow the network to pass the input data through multiple layers without the risk of vanishing gradients, making it easier for the network to learn complex relationships between the input and output data.",
    "• End-to-end learning: With the combination of residual connections and channel attention, the ResNet with channel attention is able to learn end-to-end from the input data to the final prediction.",
    "This makes the network more flexible and capable of adapting to different input distributions and learning more complex representations of the data.",
    "• The effectiveness of the proposed model and its ability to achieve better image classification results compared with previous state-of-the-art approaches has been demonstrated through extensive experiments on three benchmark datasets."
